Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.redis.client

Class RedisClientConnection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bluezoo.gumdrop.Connection
      • org.bluezoo.gumdrop.redis.client.RedisClientConnection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChannelHandler, RedisSession
    public class RedisClientConnection
extends Connection
implements RedisSession
    Event-driven, NIO-based Redis client connection.

    This connection handles the Redis protocol using RESP encoding/decoding and integrates with Gumdrop's asynchronous I/O framework.

    Commands are queued and matched with responses in order. Multiple commands can be outstanding simultaneously (pipelining).

    Author:
    Chris Burdess
